Get win probability chart data from ESPN

cfb_metrics_espn_wp.Rd

Graciously contributed by MrCaseB:

cfb_metrics_espn_wp(game_id)

Arguments

game_id

(Integer required): Game ID filter for querying a single game
Can be found using the cfbscrapR::cfb_game_info() function

Source

https://gist.github.com/mrcaseb/0f868193affb4be152e8e82c43a4dc07

Value

A data frame with 5 variables:

espn_game_id

character.

play_id

character.

seconds_left

integer.

home_win_percentage

double.

away_win_percentage

double.

Examples
